Member Function Documentation

writeNext ( $  item = false  ) 

Write the next entity.

This method can only be invoked after CMFileWriter::prepareWriteFile() but before CMFileWriter::finishWriteFile(). Depending on the application it can be invoked zero or more times.

Parameters:
$item The data type and value of $item is specific to what the inheriting class expects. See the documentation for each subclass.
Returns:
true on success, otherwise false.

Implemented in CMFileCSV, CMFileICAL, and CMFileVCF.
